-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; background-color: #eeedeb; background-size: 22px; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: 483.75px !important; width: 645px !important; border: 1px solid #eeedeb;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoa7tIUe6qc8GkGVxVtZ77eSOKiaR5AicIKxF9n7hWApW5bEzultjZUcicnA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="407" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoa7tIUe6qc8GkGVxVtZ77eSOKiaR5AicIKxF9n7hWApW5bEzultjZUcicnA/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: #888888;">图/cegoh</span></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">客家酿豆腐</strong>是客家名菜之一。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">传说酿豆腐源于北方的饺子，因岭南地方少麦，客家移民便以豆腐替代面粉，将肉馅塞入豆腐中，犹如面粉裹着肉馅。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaGtkFkKypHRR6ra8BJA7Buuwaf3aNpE87rGyicsn7VHxQZUvYLSbSJ3Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="407" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaGtkFkKypHRR6ra8BJA7Buuwaf3aNpE87rGyicsn7VHxQZUvYLSbSJ3Q/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: #888888;">▲客家酿豆腐 图/摄图网@竹林惜月</span></p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">制作酿豆腐，就是往豆腐里填入腌制过的馅料，再将酿好的豆腐过油煎，吃的时候，外面的豆腐脆脆的，里面却很嫩滑，再加上鲜美的酿馅，让人爱不释口。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="__bg_gif" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; color: #595959; font-size: 14px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, &#x27;PingFang SC&#x27;, &#x27;Hiragino Sans GB&#x27;, &#x27;Microsoft YaHei UI&#x27;, &#x27;Microsoft YaHei&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/b8ezmQwia6xiaeRPHxibyHVeWKZzicMNEibrWefSPwyMgjdL4ujJR1PKcFb1E0WPRS2GKBKvQshibCMIibRZlBX5crccQ/640?wx_fmt=gif" width="491" data-backh="353" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/b8ezmQwia6xiaeRPHxibyHVeWKZzicMNEibrWefSPwyMgjdL4ujJR1PKcFb1E0WPRS2GKBKvQshibCMIibRZlBX5crccQ/?wx_fmt=gif" data-copyright="0" data-type="gif" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">漂泊在他乡的客家人，吃上一口酿豆腐，亲切得就像回到了家。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">而酿的做法，也能延伸到茄子、苦瓜上，再加上酿豆腐，这三道酿菜一起被称为&ldquo;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">煎酿三宝</strong>&rdquo;。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhEJ8jeic5xqlAOOPC32BGiafEIiczwaNkK50xs8Phiblas6jQ5DIiaprxwvK0CicyQKDnIghBMj5IYyxzA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1018" data-backh="373" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhEJ8jeic5xqlAOOPC32BGiafEIiczwaNkK50xs8Phiblas6jQ5DIiaprxwvK0CicyQKDnIghBMj5IYyxzA/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">不过&ldquo;酿&rdquo;这个字的最高境界，大概表现在惠州的一道名菜中，那就是&ldquo;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">酿春</strong>&rdquo;。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">&ldquo;酿春&rdquo;是指在生蛋中加入肉馅，这道菜曾经登上了央视的《中国味道》栏目。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"> </span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="raw-image" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: middle; width: 497px; height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/71vT6WeWUCXiaoy7y5hAIcibv7xNJ7c2HUsd7kLibWl2jXN3HkrKlqicib5BP4MoChDjPCGVicsFEb5InHdp7Hnnmbcw/640?wx_fmt=gif" width="400" data-backh="324" data-backw="574" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/71vT6WeWUCXiaoy7y5hAIcibv7xNJ7c2HUsd7kLibWl2jXN3HkrKlqicib5BP4MoChDjPCGVicsFEb5InHdp7Hnnmbcw/?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-role="outer">\n<section class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;">\n<section class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-role="paragraph">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">在惠州话中，&ldquo;春&rdquo;与&ldquo;蛋&rdquo;同音，酿春即是酿蛋，主要是孩子生日时加的一道菜，平时不太常见。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">酿春一般选用鸭蛋，先把生鸭蛋整只打入碗中，然后用筷子轻轻挑开蛋黄上的层皮，慢慢将肉馅酿入整个蛋黄的中间。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; background-color: #eeedeb; background-size: 22px; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: 354.75px !important; width: 645px !important; border: 1px solid #eeedeb;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaMkch8U8bDq8SO0vneMKlsevuS3rS4rnT6rq7uQZ07yj803ITq1I0Jw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="700" data-backh="298" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaMkch8U8bDq8SO0vneMKlsevuS3rS4rnT6rq7uQZ07yj803ITq1I0Jw/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">除此之外，还有<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">酿莲藕、酿青椒、酿香菇</strong>&hellip;&hellip;</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/71vT6WeWUCXiaoy7y5hAIcibv7xNJ7c2HUhptvC27GdbMBdmuricMk57BWjjATEda1r4FLh5hZic9cGBcrXSictDUqg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1080" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-role="outer">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-role="outer">\n<section class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-id="93278">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-width="100%">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-width="50%">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-width="100%">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">可以说，客家人是看见什么酿什么！</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/71vT6WeWUCXiaoy7y5hAIcibv7xNJ7c2HUibt5AWrxCmTuQ9BgR8g6jsteRHCkDGavMCQhaDGWhice5gmlZB6fVIMQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="702" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;" data-role="paragraph">\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">此外，客家人还喜欢咸菜、梅菜等盐渍食品。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">不得不说的就是<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">梅菜扣肉</strong>，也称咸烧白，这是一道肥而不腻的下饭菜。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">扣肉颜色酱红鲜亮，看似油腻的肥肉，实则滑溜醇香。五花肉里带着梅菜的清香，梅菜吸收了油脂，又不会有流油的肥腻感。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages  __bg_gif" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaRNavP8Gg76mLYXYDJmfsq855HW14AEDqtHQd1fCAUMnH9KdCNplOhw/640?wx_fmt=gif" width="639" data-backh="362" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaRNavP8Gg76mLYXYDJmfsq855HW14AEDqtHQd1fCAUMnH9KdCNplOhw/?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" /></p>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #888888; font-size: 12px;">图/摄图网@夏花</span></p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">而其中的灵魂梅菜，就是广东惠州的客家特产，以鲜梅菜为原料经腌制后再脱盐等工艺制成，被誉为岭南三大名菜之一，历史上还曾作为宫廷食品，被称为"惠州贡菜"。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaNTCkYjQMibFT8uQNZnVVFmCHWO0Zbl0wibPHlfXibpkfhIkytBheu9w9g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="816" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaNTCkYjQMibFT8uQNZnVVFmCHWO0Zbl0wibPHlfXibpkfhIkytBheu9w9g/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: #888888;">图/摄图网@崇极技术杨</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">&ldquo;咸菜&rdquo;的另一代表，就是上过《舌尖上的中国》的<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">盐焗鸡</strong>了，以盐焗鸡为代表的东江菜，属于客家菜里的水系流派。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaL1PkDB0N6SiayRLuRAFgN7JcQCKeCRibpjDDmbJiaXkt2R5rEIsvicVvQA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="361" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaL1PkDB0N6SiayRLuRAFgN7JcQCKeCRibpjDDmbJiaXkt2R5rEIsvicVvQA/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">盐焗鸡有<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">手撕</strong>和<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">切块</strong>两种处理方法&mdash;&mdash;传统客家人爱手撕，这样能避免鸡肉纤维遭到破坏；而斩块的盐焗鸡连肉带骨，吃起来更香。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">一般酒店会奉上一碟用鸡油和沙姜粉混合的咸味蘸料，香得你能多吃两钵米饭；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">若是到了梅州街边的盐焗鸡小店，店家还卖你一碗鸡汤粉。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">吃鸡肉，嚼鸡杂，吸米线，喝鸡汤，印证了客家人喜好&ldquo;肥、咸、熟、香&rdquo;的饮食特点。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">说到鸡，不能遗忘的还有客家<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">猪肚鸡</strong>，这可是秋冬时节最暖心暖胃的存在。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">猪肚鸡又名&ldquo;凤凰投胎&rdquo;，是客家地区酒席必备的餐前用汤，汤里有浓郁的药材味和胡椒香气，一口下肚，瞬间就能振奋食欲。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages __bg_gif" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; background-size: 22px; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; text-align: center; height: 453.811px !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 645px !important; border: 1px solid #eeedeb;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/qgj53NGEnUTv8p7UgBfR31bkE8djSdxzmgqZePmk0K619Zboapjj9ptryDNy8xUnC9lYZrsSX4HMov84wTKmicw/640?wx_fmt=gif" width="614" data-backh="381" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/qgj53NGEnUTv8p7UgBfR31bkE8djSdxzmgqZePmk0K619Zboapjj9ptryDNy8xUnC9lYZrsSX4HMov84wTKmicw/?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" /></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">除此之外还有<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">客家三杯鸡</strong>，&ldquo;三杯&rdquo;的含义是因为用料中有&ldquo;酱油、食油、米酒各一杯&rdquo;。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">后来，客家人将三杯鸡带到台湾，用黑麻油（或香油）代替猪油，同时加入罗勒（九层塔）提升香气，从而成为了当地的一道经典名菜，享誉世界。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PWhicyNiaYtVQvaYYHgINaLjNMQfjqNal7icWEnyjfdmxzxXZerDm1rQTA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="542" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PWhicyNiaYtVQvaYYHgINaLjNMQfjqNal7icWEnyjfdmxzxXZerDm1rQTA/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">客家人淳朴暖心，同时他们也热情好客，以擂茶待客更是传统的普遍礼节，无论是婚嫁喜庆，还是亲朋好友来访，都会请喝<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">擂茶</strong>。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">擂茶又叫&ldquo;咸茶&rdquo;、&ldquo;盐茶&rdquo;，流行于广东潮汕、揭西等地。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; background-size: 22px; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: 427.543px !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 645px !important; border: 1px solid #eeedeb;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MgQJicklZNrRiaTF3OmWvF7UHrXlGzc2kibPZ4ZvZS0osut2TMSYEOrNfkdllny74KSktCUpsm6tq6GQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="700" data-backh="359" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MgQJicklZNrRiaTF3OmWvF7UHrXlGzc2kibPZ4ZvZS0osut2TMSYEOrNfkdllny74KSktCUpsm6tq6GQ/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">这种茶的精髓在于一个&ldquo;擂&rdquo;字，也就是研磨，就是把茶叶、芝麻、花生等原料放进擂钵里，研磨捣烂成糊状后再冲开水喝。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaicehR5JDHI1JOibehRbVAVicP8VfaeR4t3smSr0nN6yGiciazM9Pkd4fH6g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="410" data-backh="308" data-backw="410" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoa0tn4duYtPIavRnuKqm3jibwz704VjbWS3YqRIpjONnRb6HiaibP1EnzOw/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-oversubscription-url="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaicehR5JDHI1JOibehRbVAVicP8VfaeR4t3smSr0nN6yGiciazM9Pkd4fH6g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">简单朴实的客家人，最擅长将简单的美食变得更加美味。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">一碗颜色金黄、味道爽口香滑的<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">梅州腌面</strong>，虽是普通的捞面，但加上葱花或芝麻，和猪油热拌，让人回味无穷。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaoqzR4UkbZr33sABqQmhAXLEn0TgRwI4afA2Vgt9fjKXNpYjbKEDm0Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="361" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoaoqzR4UkbZr33sABqQmhAXLEn0TgRwI4afA2Vgt9fjKXNpYjbKEDm0Q/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #888888; font-size: 12px;">图/icybutterfly</span></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">再加一份猪肉、猪肝、猪粉肠、枸札叶煮成的&ldquo;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">三及第汤</strong>&rdquo;，加入几滴酒糟，一面一汤，便是客家人的传统早餐。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">何为三及第？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">因为在科举取士时代，状元、榜眼、探花为殿试头三名，合称三及第，后人就把用猪肉、猪肝、猪粉肠三种猪内脏比作三及第，这也象征着客家人奋发图强，耕读传家。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoa0FaC8vOQYY5kVqYzZ9KdZLYykWXIJbLt8hZK4peNibuJplzryVTwO5Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="700" data-backh="415" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2MhR79PhQUHVj303OmDnOLoa0FaC8vOQYY5kVqYzZ9KdZLYykWXIJbLt8hZK4peNibuJplzryVTwO5Q/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">客家人爱吃<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">捶丸</strong>，也就是肉丸，客家人取&ldquo;丸&rdquo;与&ldquo;圆&rdquo;同音，寓意团圆、圆满。</span></section>\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; font-size: 16px;"> </p>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">像大家熟知的牛肉丸，很多人以为是潮州菜，但其实是正宗客家菜。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PxUaAIQEXT5CjepoBfcNA8jXWSt3zy5H7LuFiaoqZ4bEouyN3xZVO78w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="1280" data-backh="362" data-backw="542" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PxUaAIQEXT5CjepoBfcNA8jXWSt3zy5H7LuFiaoqZ4bEouyN3xZVO78w/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" /></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: #888888;">图/摄图网@大力金刚</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">其中猪肉丸、牛肉丸、牛筋丸被成为客家三大丸。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;">刚做好的猪肉丸、牛肉丸或牛筋丸，混一起煮汤，洒上少许香菜、葱花、胡椒粉等调料，就能做成一碗鲜美爽口的<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">三丸汤</strong>。</span></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"></section>\n<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; width: 645px; visibility: visible !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PgUyTjG1B8qibhwQqLicAia5NKkKLHxpuXELKlKXDxOVljWL46faXF8K4w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="500" data-backh="333" data-backw="500" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PIoiapF5EEm7DkfcLMEniaLJC70dDcD7KhMdibBPFDibqDa5h8PwBcmPtRg/?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-oversubscription-url="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0YsAA7Mh2Mia2qdticLCuoUVv3qS3wIp8PgUyTjG1B8qibhwQqLicAia5NKk